  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, there is a shortage of tools that aid in upholding principles like data quality, prevention, agency, or inclusion.",
    "These principles are highly significant in fostering confidence while dealing with sensitive data and responding to public sector initiatives.",
    "Autonomy, a principle in about 10% of all tools, is often neglected.",
    "Ensuring individuals are well-informed and free to make their own decisions is crucial.",
    "A system based on AI that \"limits people's autonomy will discriminate against them, and if these discriminations are not addressed, they will not be detected nor made visible\" (Subías-Beltrán et al. 2022, p. 15)."
  ],
